e base.</p><p> </p>","Stratford-on-Avon","Nadhim Zahawi","174793","2018-10-11T08:03:08.907Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/973378/answer","Biography information for Nadhim Zahawi","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/973378/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/973378/answer",,,,,"60","Education","Education","2018-09-13","Children: Day Care","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, with reference to his Department's publication, Evaluation of the first year of the national rollout of 30 hours free childcare, published in September 2018, whether he plans to provide additional funding to ensure that childcare providers do not suffer a loss in profit or report that they are only breaking even as a result of offering extended hours of childcare.","false","Biography information for Tulip Siddiq","Hampstead and Kilburn","Tulip Siddiq","174794"
